: 1184, \"to\": 1224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is Turkey's first medal in Olympic shooting.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9999914674727048, \"rank\": 8.451540831863937e-06, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic shooting\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many shooters at the Olympic shooting range in Chateauroux, central France, choose to wear regulation visors, also called blinders, over one eye to reduce glare and get better focus.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999599464654323, \"rank\": 0.00040065829826789126, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many shooters\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic shooting range\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"Chateauroux\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"regulation visors\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"blinders\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"one eye\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"glare\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"better focus\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He chose not to and shot with both eyes open.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both eyes\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While photos made it look like he wasn't protecting his ears during the competition, Dikec was actually wearing yellow earplugs during the finals.\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"his ears\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"yellow earplugs\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the earplugs were not visible in the image that went viral.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the earplugs\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dikec finished 13th in the singles and has now completed his run at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"the singles\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"his run\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's looking ahead to the next games in 2028.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next games\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope to win a gold medal next time in Los Angeles,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 9.807123427099165e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bonus Trivia Like Dikec, his partner Sevval Ilayda Tarhan also adopted a \\\"casual\\\" style of shooting with her hands in her pockets.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2067, \"entit